Package: dartRstartup
Title: This package loads the markdown worked examples and exercises into the Tutorial window of RStudio as a companion to the eBook Getting Started with dartR.
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Emily", "Stringer", role = "aut",
